{"id": 2338, "genre": 1001, "title": "你在生活中最常听到的“大人物”式言论是什么？", "description": "其实区别就是看待人生时，用的是主角视角还是NPC视角。（题图来自：视觉中国）", "record_count": 3058, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20180509142122vXcSE80q7DVhd39j.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-06-21T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 288770, "content": "你这样以后是要吃大亏的", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1380666}, {"id": 289029, "content": "我吃的盐比你吃的饭还多", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1382811}, {"id": 288518, "content": "1", "image": "img/option/option/20180621161516OlgbBhzNJaq8P3QV.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1359687}, {"id": 288519, "content": "我们要做爆款！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1216914}, {"id": 289034, "content": "愿尽绵薄之力。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1382911}, {"id": 292107, "content": "公司给了你这么好的平台，不要太过在意薪酬问题", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1297494}, {"id": 288782, "content": "等你以后有孩子就知道了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1360939}, {"id": 288527, "content": "我要是你，肯定不会这样做\n我要是你，肯定能做的更好\nmmp，你怎么不来", "image": null, "praise_count": 16, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 533562}, {"id": 288783, "content": "等你长大就知道了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1380704}, {"id": 288529, "content": "等你有了孩子就不这么想了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1376703}, {"id": 288530, "content": "没什么不可以的！", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1085515}, {"id": 288531, "content": "too young，too……", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1362766}, {"id": 288536, "content": "“不要乱同情别人”", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1379637}, {"id": 288540, "content": "一个人的命运，当然要靠自我奋斗，但也要考虑到.....", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 792896}, {"id": 288541, "content": "其实我想唱个反调…我觉得有时候回顾，前辈说的有些，确实一一应验了???", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1082087}, {"id": 288542, "content": "等以后你就知道了", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1258692}, {"id": 288544, "content": "多一条人脉多一个路子。", "image": null, "praise_count": 25, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1378905}, {"id": 288545, "content": "越大越不听话", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1379681}, {"id": 288546, "content": "这个套路不对", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1293730}, {"id": 288547, "content": "你先按我说的做，以后你就明白了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1379683}, {"id": 288548, "content": "我有个朋友……", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1323427}, {"id": 289060, "content": "等你有了钱 你也会包二奶 换老婆 走到哪都牛哄哄的等等 只是因为你没钱 ！ 我只想回一句 “劳资就不” ", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1273401}, {"id": 288550, "content": "我要是你啊…\n你要像我这样想…", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1379686}, {"id": 291622, "content": "追随自己的内心", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1231418}, {"id": 288551, "content": "女人迟早都要当妈妈的", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 680675}, {"id": 288553, "content": "很好与优秀只差一点距离，这个距离叫安全?", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 697466}, {"id": 288555, "content": "接下来我简单地说两句", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 747131}, {"id": 288556, "content": "我从来都不喜欢钱；\n定一个小目标，先挣一个亿", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1379712}, {"id": 288558, "content": "长大之后，你就懂了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1371536}, {"id": 288559, "content": "民主", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1378898}, {"id": 288560, "content": "学历什么的其实不是很重要，关键要看人脉", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1379727}, {"id": 288563, "content": "军队一律不得经商，这个对军队的命运啊是很重要的。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1287668}, {"id": 288564, "content": "你以后就会知道我的良苦用心了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1379744}, {"id": 288565, "content": "读书没什么卵用，赚到钱才是王道", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1034180}, {"id": 288566, "content": "等你到我这个年龄你就知道了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 949989}, {"id": 288570, "content": "这题肯定不考", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1379753}, {"id": 288571, "content": "我简单说两句，啊，简单说两句。首先大家要重视这个问题，啊，重视这个问题。要上升到政治的高度，啊，政治的高度……………………………", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1378938}, {"id": 288572, "content": "等你到了我这个年龄……", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1379787}, {"id": 288573, "content": " 老实人", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1361359}, {"id": 289085, "content": "我现在简短地开个班会啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1383194}, {"id": 280894, "content": "“等你到了那个位置，你也会这样做的。”", "image": null, "praise_count": 516, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 288574, "content": "等你到了我这个年纪你也会想我这么想", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 817050}, {"id": 280895, "content": "“离开了集体/学校/公司，你什么都不是。”", "image": null, "praise_count": 336, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 288575, "content": "你以为的你以为，就是你以为的？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1251202}, {"id": 304959, "content": "你懂多少爱与恨？！？！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1369865}, {"id": 280896, "content": "“太善良的人是成不了大事的。”", "image": null, "praise_count": 240, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 288576, "content": "做人的目的是为了成为非人", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1379814}, {"id": 280898, "content": "“格局决定眼界”“格局决定思维”……总之格局决定一切。", "image": null, "praise_count": 320, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 288578, "content": "你踏入社会就知道了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1372396}, {"id": 290882, "content": "好好学习天天向上", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1382744}]}